description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=1/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=1/3. This is a side-scrolling action game.  This game has 12 Levels.You must find the key which can open the door to exit. You can stamp monstors, get your coins.If 100 coin is collected, it is exchangeable for a treasure box. If it clears once, difficult stage composition can be played. It created by action game maker.
